{"TopicId":201943,"ForumId":81,"TopicTitle":"Camera stuck mid-flight.","CreatedByName":"Wizard Kerbal","CreatedById":209063,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-23T20:33:22Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Wizard Kerbal","CreatedById":209063,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-23T20:33:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m doing my submission for\u00A0Weak Player\u0027s Micro sized distance challenge. a 0.625m challenge, and I reload a quicksave because I wasn\u0027t filming. And- my camera is stuck.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can do anything I want with my cursor and select the direction things (Stability Assist,\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:maneuver:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/Maneuver20px.png\u0022 title=\u0022:maneuver:\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:prograde:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/prograde3.png\u0022 title=\u0022:prograde:\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:retrograde:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/retrograde2.png\u0022 title=\u0022:retrograde:\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:antinormal:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/Antinormal20px.png\u0022 title=\u0022:antinormal:\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:normal:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/Normal20px.png\u0022 title=\u0022:normal:\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:antiradial:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/Antiradial20px.png\u0022 title=\u0022:antiradial:\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:radial:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/Radial20px.png\u0022 title=\u0022:radial:\u0022\u003E), but I can\u0027t move my camera, select/deselect docking mode, toggle map, or maneuver node, can\u0027t use presets. Nor can I pause.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s like i\u0027m in time warp, but i\u0027m not and can only use phys warp. All I can do is spin around the Nav-ball and watch Minmus draw ever closer.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAaaaaaaaaand, when I return to main menu none of the buttons there work either. KSP CONSOLE IS SO MUCH FUN\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-04-23T20:59:27Z\u0022 title=\u002204/23/2021 08:59  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EApril 23, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by Wizard Kerbal\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EI can pause by pressing home. Still doesn\u0026#039;t help when I reload a quick save.\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"An Amongus Sussy Player","CreatedById":210950,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-05T08:55:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/209063-wizard-kerbal/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022209063\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/209063-wizard-kerbal/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Wizard Kerbal\u003C/a\u003E Its probably due to action sets menu being opened\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Wizard Kerbal","CreatedById":209063,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-05T13:37:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey weren\u2019t\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dr. Kerbal","CreatedById":207217,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-17T17:09:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAh! This happnes to me on the PS4 and the PC. The camer will just get stuck and nothing will open as the craft flys. The best way to fix this is to restart your console.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}